    <text type="card">
        <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_4_00033"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb338" type="place">I Wollzeile 15</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1894_AS_RBH_4_00034"/>Samſtag</dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Richard. </salute>Ich bin heut beim <rs ref="#pmb42186" type="work">Doppelſelbſtmord</rs>, da<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> im <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34" type="place">Griensteidl</rs></hi>. Was morgen mit der <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL20191014-3"/><rs ref="#pmb40" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Josefstadt</hi></rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL20191014-3h">Am Nachmittag fand die Première des Mimodramas <rs ref="#pmb30411" type="work">Der Buckelhans</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb42193" type="person">Pierre Blanchard de la Bretesche</rs> statt.</note> los, weiſs ich noch nicht; <rs ref="#pmb11740" type="person">Hugo</rs> hat mir geſagt, dſs er ko<c rendition="#gemination-m"/>t.</p>
<closer>Herzlich Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body>
